M|4-La|tx|```
M|4-La|tx|Browser (rc)
M|4-La|tx|↓
M|4-La|tx|nx.js ap rt (/app/ap/*/rt.ts)
M|4-La|tx|↓
M|4-La|tx|External Services (Anthropic \| Apify \| YouTube \| GA4 \| sb)
