M|4-La|it|ap keys live only in nx.js ap rt — never in client cp.
M|4-La|it|sb `service_role` key used only server-side. Browser uses `anon` key via `createBrowserClient`.
M|4-La|it|Persistent data always in sb. `localStorage` only for ephemeral UI state (tab position, scroll).
M|Comp|tx|\| tp \| When to use \| Rule \|
M|Comp|tx|\|------\|------------\|------\|
M|Comp|tx|\| Server cp (default) \| Data fetching, no us interaction \| No `'use client'` directive \|
M|Comp|tx|\| Client cp \| State, event handlers, browser APIs \| Add `'use client'` at top of file only \|
M|Comp|tx|\| rt Handler \| External ap calls, DB writes \| In `/app/ap/*/rt.ts` only \|
M|Comp|tx|> `'use client'` boundary shd be as deep in the cp tree as possible. Never mark a layout or wrapper as client unless required.
