M|Writ|it|Milestone → tasks → owners → dependencies. Each task has exactly one owner.
M|Writ|it|Surface blockers and risks — not just the steps.
M|Writ|- **|plans w/o explicit owners or unresolved dependency chains.
M|Exec|it|Verify plan state before the first step. Check dependencies before starting each task.
M|Exec|it|up the plan after each done task — never let it go stale.
M|Exec|- **|marking a task complete w/o verifying its output.
M|Brai|it|Diverge → cluster → converge. Quantity before qual in the generation phase.
M|Brai|it|No criticism during diverge — every option gets written down first.
M|Brai|- **|evaluating approaches before the generation phase is complete.
M|Syst|it|Reproduce → isolate → hypothesize → tst → document. Never skip reproduce.
M|Syst|it|Document the root cause, not just the fix — future dv will need to understand why.
M|Syst|- **|fixing symptoms w/o understanding what caused them.
M|Test|it|Red → green → rf. Write the failing tst before the implementation.
M|Test|it|tst behavior, not implementation detail. Each tst has one assertion.
M|Test|- **|tests that pass trivially or tst internal state rather than external behavior.
M|Requ|it|Context → what changed → what to focus on. Flag specific uncertainty areas explicitly.
M|Requ|it|Provide the PR link, relevant diff sections, and the acceptance criteria being met.
M|Requ|- **|PRs w/ no description — reviewers need context.
M|Rece|it|Respond to every comment. "Won't fix" requires an explanation, not silence.
M|Rece|it|Separate clarifying questions from disagreements — ask first, then decide.
M|Rece|- **|defensive rp; treat every comment as useful signal.
M|Veri|it|bd passes (`npm run bd` zero er). Lint passes (`npm run lint` zero warnings). Browser-verified for UI changes.
M|Veri|it|No feature ships w/o evidence of verification.
M|Veri|- **|marking done w/o running bd and lint in the same sn.
M|Disp|it|Define ag role, input, output format, and handoff criteria before spawning.
M|Disp|it|Merge outputs before responding — never surface raw parallel ag output directly.
M|Disp|- **|dispatching w/ unresolved dependencies btw workstreams.
M|Usin|it|One worktree per feature. Never commit directly to main from a worktree.
M|Usin|it|Clean up worktrees after the branch is merged.
M|Usin|- **|long-lived worktrees that drift far from the main branch.
M|Fini|- Sq|`tp(scope): description`.
M|Fini|it|dl the branch after merge. up MEMORY.md w/ completion status.
M|Fini|- **|merging w/o qn's APPROVED verdict.
M|Suba|it|Define ag role + expected output format before spawning.
M|Suba|it|Verify subagent output before integrating — treat it as a PR, not a done deal.
M|Suba|- **|chaining subagent outputs w/o a verification step btw them.
M|Supa|it|Server-side client w/ service role key for writes. RLS for us-scoped reads.
M|Supa|it|Index on frequently queried foreign keys. Prefer typed queries over raw SQL strings.
M|Supa|- **|exposing `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` to client cp.
M|Verc|it|Server cp by default. `'use client'` only when interactivity or browser APIs are required.
M|Verc|it|No secrets in client cp — all external ap calls go through `/app/ap/` rt.
M|Verc|- **|unnecessary `useEffect` for data that can be fetched in a Server cp.
M|Verc|it|Parallel data fetching in Server cp. Streaming w/ `Suspense` for slow data.
M|Verc|it|Collocate data fetching w/ the cp that uses it — don't prop-drill fetched data.
M|Verc|- **|request waterfalls in RSC trees; fetch all independent data in parallel.